sentences: In 2009, as part of the collective The Lappetites, she staged the multimedia opera 'Fathers' in Berlin Haus der Kulturen der Welt.
In 2011 she initiated the arts organization Hai Art on the island of Hailuoto and acts as curator and executive producer since.
She lived in Berlin from 1996 to 2008.
In 2008 she moved to Hailuoto, Finland.
